        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1358196185" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15270667652202484798">A short review for a short novel.<br/><br/>As French things go, this one went too. Delicate in its aesthetics, bold in ideas and a little silly in its notions of love. A petite and accessible tale of love and its labours lost and a simultaneous ode into dejection. <br/><br/>For me, this serves as an introduction to Gide before I read the more serious work that is &apos;The Counterfeiters&apos;.</span>
  <span id="freeText15270667652202484798" style="display:none">A short review for a short novel.<br /><br />As French things go, this one went too. Delicate in its aesthetics, bold in ideas and a little silly in its notions of love. A petite and accessible tale of love and its labours lost and a simultaneous ode into dejection. <br /><br />For me, this serves as an introduction to Gide before I read the more serious work that is 'The Counterfeiters'.</span>
  <a data-text-id="15270667652202484798" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


