<span id="freeTextContainer6447696556998260250">I read this book when I was very very young. To this day it is one of the saddest books I&apos;ve read. <br/>It is philosophical, I know that, I know that there is a message there, I get that. But the young me hated how very tragic everything was. <br/>It is so beautifully written. It will touch your soul and leave you thinking for months after.</span>
  <span id="freeText6447696556998260250" style="display:none">I read this book when I was very very young. To this day it is one of the saddest books I've read. <br />It is philosophical, I know that, I know that there is a message there, I get that. But the young me hated how very tragic everything was. <br />It is so beautifully written. It will touch your soul and leave you thinking for months after.</span>
